metadata.name: E. Weiss: Frequency - 2022
metadata.description:
If a friend falls, forgive them and lift them up. We all fall and are in need of a hand from time to time. Share your burdens, your stories, your feelings; complete the connection. Look inside and find your assignment. Focus on that work and avoid distractions of the ego. Do not compare yourself to others. Live creatively. 

‭‭Galatians‬ ‭6:1-5‬
